Apa maksudnya?

213
00:16:26,618 --> 00:16:29,420
Semuanya mati.

214
00:16:30,556 --> 00:16:32,690
Bohong.

215
00:16:32,692 --> 00:16:36,461
Tak ada yang tersisa?
Hanya kau?

216
00:16:36,463 --> 00:16:37,562
Aku.

217
00:16:37,564 --> 00:16:41,432
Sang raja.

218
00:16:41,434 --> 00:16:44,235
Pria berkapak.

219
00:16:44,237 --> 00:16:46,537
Dan wanita gila berambut pendek.

220
00:16:49,708 --> 00:16:51,209
Kau yang melakukan ini.

221
00:16:53,313 --> 00:16:57,215
Kelompokku.

222
00:16:57,217 --> 00:17:01,519
Kelompokmu.

223
00:17:01,521 --> 00:17:03,187
Mereka semua tewas.

224
00:17:13,399 --> 00:17:15,633
Sial.

225
00:17:19,538 --> 00:17:24,475
Dan sekarang, aku juga.

226
00:17:42,294 --> 00:17:44,462
Kita bisa menunggu sebentar...

227
00:17:44,464 --> 00:17:48,766
...siapa tahu orang-orangku
bisa mencari jalan keluar.

228
00:17:48,768 --> 00:17:52,737
Satu hal yang pasti...

229
00:17:52,739 --> 00:17:56,841
...jika orang-orangku
mengira aku mati...

230
00:17:56,843 --> 00:18:00,445
...banyak orang yang akan
mati di sana.

231
00:18:00,447 --> 00:18:02,113
